summary: Greece athletes call for more support
title: Greece athletes call for more support
description:
Some of Greece’s star athletes are blaming a lack of financial support and state negligence for having a negative effect on their careers.

They say there needs to be more focus on supporting them and providing adequate facilities for them to focus on training and excelling.
